Classes in alphabetsoup.base used by alphabetsoup.base
BucketbotBase
          BucketbotBase provides the basic functionality for a passive bucketbot.
BucketbotBase.BucketbotState
          BucketbotState is interface which should be inherited to provied states for the Bucketbot to be in.
BucketbotTask
          BucketbotTask is a class which describes the major tasks which can be "physically" completed (physically meaning via bucketbots, buckets, and stations).
BucketbotTask.TaskType
          TaskType is the type of task, and indicates the meaning of each of the fields of this class.
 

Classes in alphabetsoup.base used by alphabetsoup.simulators.combinatorialmarkettaskallocation
BucketBase
          BucketBase is the basic and fully capable implementation of a passive Bucket.
LetterStationBase
          LetterStationBase implements the basic functionality of a passive Letter station, such that it can receive letters when given them by the system, and will place letters in buckets when requested to do so.
WordStationBase
          WordStationBase implements the basic functionality of a passive Word station, such that it can take letters from buckets when requested, clears words when complete, and can be assigned new words when space permits.
